==English==

=== Pronunciation ===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /'gʌl/

=== Noun ===
'''gull'''
# A [[seabird]] of the genus ''Larus'' or of the family Laridae.
# (''slang'') A cheating trick; a [[fraud]].
#* One easily cheated; a [[dupe]].

=== Synonyms ===
*[[mew]]
*[[seagull]]

